OL,3,CReeves to outline plans to protect
OL,4,Cpublic from unfair price hikes
OL,6,FRachel Reeves will outline plans to
OL,7,Fguard against unfair price rises amid
OL,8,Ffears among the public over surging
OL,9,Foil and fuel prices sparked by the
OL,10,FIran war.
OL,12,FThe Chancellor will make a statement
OL,13,Fto MPs after laying out her plans to
OL,14,Fthe Prime Minister and colleagues in
OL,15,Fan emergency Cobra meeting on Monday
OL,16,Fafternoon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
