OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774365082
OL,3,CReeves to outline plans to protect
OL,4,Cpublic from unfair price hikes
OL,6,FThose will include an "anti-
OL,7,Fprofiteering framework" to detect and
OL,8,Fcrack down on companies exploiting the
OL,9,FMiddle East crisis and help the
OL,10,FCompetition and Markets Authority root
OL,11,Fout price gouging.
OL,13,FIt comes after Sir Keir Starmer said
OL,14,Fhe was looking at boosting the
OL,15,Fcompetition regulator's powers, giving
OL,16,Fit "further teeth" to deal with
OL,17,Fprofiteering.
OL,26,@nD@WOUoD@WO]xD@DOUxD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
