CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774365082
OL,3,CReeves to outline plans to protect
OL,4,Cpublic from unfair price hikes
OL,6,FThis could involve giving regulators
OL,7,F"time-limited, targeted powers" and
OL,8,Fthe Treasury, Department for Business
OL,9,Fand Trade and regulators were said to
OL,10,Fbe working "at pace" on what those
OL,11,Fpowers could be.
OL,13,FThe Chancellor is also expected to
OL,14,Ftell the Commons that Britain needs a
OL,15,Fdiverse mix of energy to shield the
OL,16,Fpublic from volatile fossil fuel
OL,17,Fmarkets and stress the importance of
OL,18,Fnot letting "blockers" get in the way
OL,19,Fof boosting Britain's nuclear power
OL,20,Fsupply.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@_O]rD@LOUrD@TO]zD@MOUzD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
