CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774365082
OL,3,CReeves to outline plans to protect
OL,4,Cpublic from unfair price hikes
OL,6,FMs Reeves will announce that she is
OL,7,Fexploring government-backed
OL,8,Findemnities for critical energy
OL,9,Fsecurity projects so construction can
OL,10,Fcontinue if a project is legally
OL,11,Fchallenged.
OL,13,FThough the US pause on strikes against
OL,14,FIranian energy infrastructure calmed
OL,15,Fmarkets and saw oil prices ease back,
OL,16,FSir Keir Starmer said Britain must be
OL,17,Fprepared for the Iran war to continue
OL,18,F"for some time" on Monday.
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
