CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774365082
OL,3,CReeves to outline plans to protect
OL,4,Cpublic from unfair price hikes
OL,6,FDonald Trump had threatened to
OL,7,Fobliterate Iranian power plants if
OL,8,FTehran did not open the Strait of
OL,9,FHormuz to shipping by 11.45pm on
OL,10,FMonday, and then said he would
OL,11,F"postpone" the strikes after "very
OL,12,Fgood and productive" talks with Tehran.
OL,14,FBut Iranian officials have denied any
OL,15,Fsuch negotiations took place.
OL,17,FThe Prime Minister insisted the UK
OL,18,Fwould not become more deeply involved
OL,19,Fin the conflict as he faced questions
OL,20,Ffrom Parliament's Liaison Committee on
OL,21,FMonday.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@JO]sD@^OUtD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
