OL,3,CReeves to outline plans to protect
OL,4,Cpublic from unfair price hikes
OL,6,FAsked about Mr Trump's recent public
OL,7,Fcomments about him and the UK, Sir
OL,8,FKeir said he was "unapologetic" about
OL,9,Fremaining focused on the British
OL,10,Fnational interest.
OL,12,F"A lot of what is said or done is
OL,13,Fundoubtedly said and done to put
OL,14,Fpressure on me. I have no doubt about
OL,15,Fthat. I understand exactly what is
OL,16,Fgoing on, but I'm not going to be
OL,17,Fwavering on this," he said.
OL,26,@pD@ROUpD@_O]tD@AOUyD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
