OL,3,CReeves to outline plans to protect
OL,4,Cpublic from unfair price hikes
OL,6,FElsewhere, the Prime Minister revealed
OL,7,Fa long-delayed defence investment plan
OL,8,Fwas now on his desk awaiting final
OL,9,Fconsideration, and suggested he
OL,10,Ffavoured closer co-operation with the
OL,11,FEU on defence in future.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, the British warship sent to
OL,14,Fthe eastern Mediterranean to defend
OL,15,FCyprus, HMS Dragon, has arrived and
OL,16,Fwill be ready to begin "operational
OL,17,Fintegration" into the island's defence
OL,18,Fon Monday night.
OL,26,@xD@XOUyD@LO]
